1
00:00:09,160 --> 00:00:14,160
<font size="20"><font face="Trebuchet MS"><b><font size="18">{\an7}Bring Despair to the Earth, and…</font></b></font></font>

2
00:00:10,730 --> 00:00:12,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Hey, does this mean...?</font>

3
00:00:12,420 --> 00:00:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}The backstage has been restored?</font>

4
00:00:14,810 --> 00:00:17,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not just that. It's calling for us.</font>

5
00:00:18,500 --> 00:00:20,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That means XENOS hasn't given up.</font>

6
00:00:30,170 --> 00:00:31,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Apollo?!</font>

7
00:00:32,340 --> 00:00:33,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It can't be...</font>

8
00:00:34,180 --> 00:00:38,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Apollo didn't trust us to do our job?</font>

9
00:00:43,460 --> 00:00:46,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's <i>you</i> he doesn't trust.</font>

10
00:00:50,530 --> 00:00:54,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}A calling arises from deep 
within in my burning heart</i></font>

11
00:00:55,530 --> 00:00:57,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's Show Time</i></font>

12
00:01:06,300 --> 00:01:09,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The price of living in the time of freedom</i></font>

13
00:01:09,290 --> 00:01:10,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}"So, what do you want to do?"</i></font>

14
00:01:10,900 --> 00:01:16,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just standing there with my empty body</i></font>

15
00:01:16,540 --> 00:01:21,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like a calling to protect the world</i></font>

16
00:01:21,030 --> 00:01:27,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I craved an unequaled gift</i></font>

17
00:01:27,430 --> 00:01:30,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Lost in night's darkness</i></font>

18
00:01:30,530 --> 00:01:34,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Until a voice called out to me</i></font>

19
00:01:34,260 --> 00:01:37,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like the light that declares the dawn</i></font>

20
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:43,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll take you with me at 
any cost (I pray and wish)</i></font>

21
00:01:41,550 --> 00:01:46,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Beyond the Echo-verse (To the future)</i></font>

22
00:01:44,620 --> 00:01:47,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just being with you makes me strong</i></font>

23
00:01:47,380 --> 00:01:48,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}It's not an exaggeration</i></font>

24
00:01:48,760 --> 00:01:53,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}That encounter was a supernova 
(Our eyes were locked)</i></font>

25
00:01:51,390 --> 00:01:56,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>In an instant, everything that I am 
(In an instant)</i></font>

26
00:01:54,750 --> 00:02:00,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Will be changed forever (Just to be)</i></font>

27
00:01:58,690 --> 00:02:02,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>A calling arises from deep
 within in my burning heart</i></font>

28
00:02:02,530 --> 00:02:04,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

29
00:02:04,990 --> 00:02:07,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be who we are</i></font>

30
00:02:07,570 --> 00:02:10,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Destiny is Calling us now</i></font>

31
00:02:10,110 --> 00:02:12,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Just to be by your side</i></font>

32
00:02:23,030 --> 00:02:24,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Mirage has exuded! 
The coordinates are...</font>

33
00:02:26,920 --> 00:02:28,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right above us?!</font>

34
00:02:29,190 --> 00:02:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Since they know the headquarters 
of SI-VIS, it was just a matter of...</font>

35
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:37,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We should probably 
think about moving, President.</font>

36
00:02:37,680 --> 00:02:39,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stage has been set 
on the rooftop of Harmonia!</font>

37
00:02:39,970 --> 00:02:41,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Connecting to the backstage!</font>

38
00:02:41,330 --> 00:02:43,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">All members are on standby!</font>

39
00:02:53,570 --> 00:02:56,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you try to start without us.</font>

40
00:02:59,600 --> 00:03:02,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're gonna pay for that later, okay?</font>

41
00:03:05,460 --> 00:03:08,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why? Why did you come?</i></font>

42
00:03:08,510 --> 00:03:11,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You physically left the home world?</i></font>

43
00:03:12,160 --> 00:03:17,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Archon is watching over
 Lady Eden. No need to worry.</font>

44
00:03:17,290 --> 00:03:19,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You don't trust me?</i></font>

45
00:03:20,630 --> 00:03:23,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I finally understand 
your thought process.</i></font>

46
00:03:23,450 --> 00:03:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can now see from the bottom 
of my heart that they're pests.</i></font>

47
00:03:26,970 --> 00:03:29,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I've finally made up 
my mind to crush them.</i></font>

48
00:03:29,830 --> 00:03:33,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'll continue to deal with Earth.</font>

49
00:03:33,830 --> 00:03:35,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But there's one thing...</font>

50
00:03:37,580 --> 00:03:40,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I need to assess it myself...</font>

51
00:03:43,070 --> 00:03:47,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Whether that girl 
is the heir to the Diva or not.</font>

52
00:03:57,270 --> 00:04:00,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idea is rising above the expected value.</font>

53
00:04:00,130 --> 00:04:02,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Twelve thousand, thirteen thousand!</font>

54
00:04:02,140 --> 00:04:04,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Go for it, everyone!</font>

55
00:04:05,230 --> 00:04:07,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hell?! Is that guy messing with us?</font>

56
00:04:08,140 --> 00:04:12,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Or he has complete confidence 
against SI-VIS.</font>

57
00:04:16,470 --> 00:04:17,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">On his own?</font>

58
00:04:17,540 --> 00:04:19,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who is that?</font>

59
00:04:19,490 --> 00:04:22,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not the pervy old man 
or the quibbling old hag.</font>

60
00:04:23,630 --> 00:04:25,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you are SI-VIS.</font>

61
00:04:26,630 --> 00:04:31,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You raise Idea by singing and 
protect your planet from your enemies.</font>

62
00:04:31,950 --> 00:04:37,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Are you the guardians of the
planet or simply drones?</font>

63
00:04:37,740 --> 00:04:41,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now we've got a senile 
armchair philosopher.</font>

64
00:04:41,100 --> 00:04:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, I saw him earlier.</font>

65
00:04:44,430 --> 00:04:46,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yosuke's old friend.</font>

66
00:04:46,590 --> 00:04:51,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, he attacked Nagi and Yosuke 
when they came to Earth. An enemy!</font>

67
00:04:51,630 --> 00:04:53,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yosuke-kun knew him?</font>

68
00:04:53,290 --> 00:04:56,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">XENOS attacked Yosuke and Nagi?</font>

69
00:04:57,140 --> 00:04:58,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Holy crap!</font>

70
00:04:58,430 --> 00:05:00,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They found out at the worst possible time!</font>

71
00:05:01,140 --> 00:05:03,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What are you going to do, President?</font>

72
00:05:03,100 --> 00:05:05,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If they get upset...</font>

73
00:05:09,680 --> 00:05:11,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Listen, everyone.</font>

74
00:05:11,070 --> 00:05:13,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yosuke and Nagi are...</font>

75
00:05:13,380 --> 00:05:17,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Um, sorry to interrupt, 
but is this gonna take long?</i></font>

76
00:05:17,700 --> 00:05:18,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?</font>

77
00:05:18,450 --> 00:05:20,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>We don't have time for that.</i></font>

78
00:05:20,290 --> 00:05:21,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Or more like...</i></font>

79
00:05:21,500 --> 00:05:23,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We don't actually care.</font>

80
00:05:24,120 --> 00:05:27,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Who Yosuke-kun and Nagi-chan really are?</font>

81
00:05:27,310 --> 00:05:29,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We know who they are.</font>

82
00:05:29,070 --> 00:05:30,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're the members of SI-VIS.</font>

83
00:05:38,640 --> 00:05:39,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone.</font>

84
00:05:40,480 --> 00:05:42,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And that's not all.</i></font>

85
00:05:42,950 --> 00:05:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>About Kyoya and Nagi...</i></font>

86
00:05:45,700 --> 00:05:48,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Huh? Hold on. That I need to hear!</i></font>

87
00:05:48,540 --> 00:05:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, Kyoya. After you hear this, you'll
know you're forever in Nagi's debt.</i></font>

88
00:05:52,870 --> 00:05:56,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Well, it's... um...</i></font>

89
00:05:56,530 --> 00:06:00,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>So Nagi-chan has dirt on Kyoya-kun.</i></font>

90
00:06:00,020 --> 00:06:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Dirt on Kyoya?!</i></font>

91
00:06:01,660 --> 00:06:03,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I can't let that go.</i></font>

92
00:06:03,510 --> 00:06:04,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>μ, give me a hint!</i></font>

93
00:06:04,610 --> 00:06:08,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You wanna hear? I'm not gonna tell you!</i></font>

94
00:06:11,720 --> 00:06:13,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry to keep you waiting.</font>

95
00:06:14,820 --> 00:06:18,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see. I will retract my earlier
statement of calling you drones.</font>

96
00:06:19,510 --> 00:06:22,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You connect with your teammates 
and improve one another.</font>

97
00:06:22,640 --> 00:06:27,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And the five of you are able to release 
Idea equal to tens of thousands of people.</font>

98
00:06:27,620 --> 00:06:32,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It wasn't a mistake to say 
you are the biggest threat we face.</font>

99
00:06:32,880 --> 00:06:35,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You come at us alone, knowing that?</font>

100
00:06:35,860 --> 00:06:39,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can use my power 
to the fullest if I'm alone.</font>

101
00:06:39,560 --> 00:06:42,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That way, I won't have to drag anyone in.</font>

102
00:06:42,750 --> 00:06:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I get it. You care for your friends.</font>

103
00:06:48,290 --> 00:06:50,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're the strongest.</font>

104
00:06:50,770 --> 00:06:53,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're the last boss, aren't you?</font>

105
00:06:53,870 --> 00:06:58,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The ranking of strength 
is a matter of opinion,</font>

106
00:06:58,470 --> 00:07:03,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but it is true that I carry the wishes of 
XENOS on my shoulders.</font>

107
00:07:03,420 --> 00:07:08,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Which means if we can handle you, 
we can protect the Earth, right?</font>

108
00:07:10,310 --> 00:07:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am called Apollo.</font>

109
00:07:13,950 --> 00:07:17,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I am Kyoya of SI-VIS.</font>

110
00:07:17,760 --> 00:07:20,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll carry on Yosuke-kun's wishes 
and protect the Earth.</i></font>

111
00:07:20,990 --> 00:07:22,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'll make sure everyone survives!</i></font>

112
00:07:23,550 --> 00:07:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi!</font>

113
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't care who you are 
or where you're from.</font>

114
00:07:28,060 --> 00:07:32,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For now, I want you 
to sing... for me, for us!</font>

115
00:07:35,860 --> 00:07:39,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes! Listen, Kyoya!</font>

116
00:07:39,650 --> 00:07:41,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Playing music!</font>

117
00:07:46,650 --> 00:07:52,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go beyond time to the Destination of Life</i></font>

118
00:07:47,370 --> 00:07:48,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The stage is set!</font>

119
00:07:48,550 --> 00:07:50,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The members are going up on the stage!</font>

120
00:07:50,160 --> 00:07:52,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idea has exceeded 30,000!</font>

121
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:54,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! We just got started!</font>

122
00:07:52,310 --> 00:07:57,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like the light that 
drives away the darkness</i></font>

123
00:07:54,620 --> 00:07:56,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it's true.</font>

124
00:07:56,960 --> 00:07:59,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This is crazy.</font>

125
00:07:57,530 --> 00:08:02,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I embrace our united wish 
and look straight ahead</i></font>

126
00:07:59,030 --> 00:08:00,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The enemy is ascending 
to the stage as well!</font>

127
00:08:00,670 --> 00:08:03,350
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's breaking through 
the outer wall of the stage!</font>

128
00:08:02,700 --> 00:08:08,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Believing in a different future</i></font>

129
00:08:08,930 --> 00:08:13,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I could see salvation beyond the darkness</i></font>

130
00:08:14,030 --> 00:08:19,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Because you noticed the presence of light</i></font>

131
00:08:19,060 --> 00:08:24,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The reason the light feels so bright</i></font>

132
00:08:24,800 --> 00:08:30,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Is because you understand the darkness</i></font>

133
00:08:31,680 --> 00:08:37,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Go across time and space 
to the Destination of Life</i></font>

134
00:08:33,030 --> 00:08:36,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone's moving so well 
as the Idea increases!</font>

135
00:08:36,160 --> 00:08:38,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The best performance we could ask for!</font>

136
00:08:37,540 --> 00:08:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Like a prayer that dispels the haze</i></font>

137
00:08:41,310 --> 00:08:42,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>That man.</i></font>

138
00:08:42,790 --> 00:08:48,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}I'll simply sing this wish by your side</i></font>

139
00:08:43,180 --> 00:08:44,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>He's doing the same thing as me.</i></font>

140
00:08:45,210 --> 00:08:47,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">One hundred twenty thousand. 
One hundred twenty-six...</font>

141
00:08:47,510 --> 00:08:49,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's going on here?!</font>

142
00:08:48,010 --> 00:08:53,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Seeking a different future</i></font>

143
00:08:49,300 --> 00:08:52,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idea is higher than ever before, 
so how are we neck and neck with him?!</font>

144
00:08:55,060 --> 00:08:58,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I see the details 
of the Idea's scatter diagram?</font>

145
00:08:58,080 --> 00:09:01,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've been trying to, 
but they're too close to each other.</font>

146
00:09:02,510 --> 00:09:04,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't tell me he's...!</font>

147
00:09:07,750 --> 00:09:09,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can't reach him?!</font>

148
00:09:09,110 --> 00:09:11,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn it, his defense is tight.</font>

149
00:09:11,890 --> 00:09:13,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't give up, guys!</font>

150
00:09:13,400 --> 00:09:15,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we keep on attacking, then surely...!</font>

151
00:09:15,390 --> 00:09:20,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}The shouts filled with desire 
as my spirit burns</i></font>

152
00:09:15,760 --> 00:09:18,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Surely what?</font>

153
00:09:20,680 --> 00:09:25,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Link together to give me strength</i></font>

154
00:09:21,640 --> 00:09:27,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just try to end this battle
before I unleash Helios on you.</font>

155
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:30,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hurry up, everyone!</font>

156
00:09:30,020 --> 00:09:30,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi?</font>

157
00:09:30,790 --> 00:09:33,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idea... It's gathering toward him.</font>

158
00:09:34,080 --> 00:09:37,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The Idea of an unbelievable 
number of people!</font>

159
00:09:39,440 --> 00:09:44,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You could see the pain in my profile</i></font>

160
00:09:44,610 --> 00:09:49,720
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Because you didn't look away 
and kept your gaze</i></font>

161
00:09:47,700 --> 00:09:53,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lord Apollo. You've finally chosen to...</font>

162
00:09:49,720 --> 00:09:55,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}You are able to keep your gaze</i></font>

163
00:09:54,110 --> 00:09:57,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not just SI-VIS's Idea that's rising?</font>

164
00:09:55,420 --> 00:10:03,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>{\an8}Because you've conquered 
and overcame your weakness</i></font>

165
00:09:57,800 --> 00:09:59,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Idea analysis is going up on screen!</font>

166
00:10:00,380 --> 00:10:02,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I've never seen this before.</font>

167
00:10:02,670 --> 00:10:06,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Neither XENOS nor the Mirage had a way 
to raise their Idea on their own.</font>

168
00:10:06,380 --> 00:10:11,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's why SI-VIS could fight against
them since we can raise our Idea.</font>

169
00:10:11,460 --> 00:10:14,780
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Does it mean they have 
a monster like Nagi on their side?</font>

170
00:10:20,640 --> 00:10:21,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?!</font>

171
00:10:21,260 --> 00:10:21,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That bastard!</font>

172
00:10:22,260 --> 00:10:26,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your wishes will never reach me.</font>

173
00:10:27,470 --> 00:10:33,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because... the wishes of all XENOS...</font>

174
00:10:35,270 --> 00:10:36,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Their Idea...</font>

175
00:10:41,870 --> 00:10:45,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's all on my shoulders!</font>

176
00:11:23,500 --> 00:11:25,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya?</font>

177
00:11:26,120 --> 00:11:27,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">μ?</font>

178
00:11:28,150 --> 00:11:29,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Soji?</font>

179
00:11:30,700 --> 00:11:32,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">June-san?</font>

180
00:11:36,010 --> 00:11:38,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This... can't be happening!</font>

181
00:11:39,710 --> 00:11:43,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I was going to take down June and SI-VIS!</font>

182
00:11:44,350 --> 00:11:45,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No. No!</font>

183
00:11:45,820 --> 00:11:49,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What was it that I wished for?!</font>

184
00:11:49,520 --> 00:11:54,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do I smile? Do I raise a cry of victory?</font>

185
00:11:54,320 --> 00:11:59,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Should I be relieved 
that the pests were crushed?</font>

186
00:12:00,290 --> 00:12:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I... Did I...</font>

187
00:12:04,680 --> 00:12:10,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did I really want something so pointless?</font>

188
00:12:12,610 --> 00:12:14,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everyone! Please respond!</font>

189
00:12:14,800 --> 00:12:18,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Kyoya! μ! Please! Say someth—</i></font>

190
00:12:18,050 --> 00:12:20,550
<font size="20"><font size="25"><font color="#c1c3c8">Please stand by</font></font></font>

191
00:12:20,550 --> 00:12:22,050
<font size="20"><font size="13"><font color="#c1c3c8">Please stand by</font></font></font>

192
00:12:22,050 --> 00:12:23,550
<font size="20"><font size="13"><font color="#c1c3c8">Please stand by</font></font></font>

193
00:12:24,060 --> 00:12:27,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya! μ! Please! Say something!</font>

194
00:12:29,870 --> 00:12:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">So you're supposed 
to be the heir to the Diva?</font>

195
00:12:35,570 --> 00:12:39,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The hope of salvation for us XENOS?</font>

196
00:12:40,150 --> 00:12:42,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Everything about you is inadequate!</font>

197
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:46,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Because you have no power, 
my comrades have fallen.</font>

198
00:12:47,770 --> 00:12:49,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me?</font>

199
00:12:49,600 --> 00:12:53,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you could control Idea at will,</font>

200
00:12:53,180 --> 00:12:56,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then even I would've found it 
difficult to defeat you.</font>

201
00:12:58,550 --> 00:13:01,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But that wasn't the case.</font>

202
00:13:08,020 --> 00:13:11,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Samael and Medea were mistaken.</font>

203
00:13:11,630 --> 00:13:16,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I fail to see the value they saw in you.</font>

204
00:13:18,870 --> 00:13:23,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Therefore, as SI-VIS, 
as a human being, you shall perish.</font>

205
00:13:31,630 --> 00:13:33,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Labyrinth, huh?</font>

206
00:13:33,790 --> 00:13:36,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What do you plan to do, 
trapping me in here...</font>

207
00:13:37,160 --> 00:13:38,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea?</font>

208
00:13:40,650 --> 00:13:45,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is too early to turn our backs on Nagi.</font>

209
00:13:45,750 --> 00:13:48,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But she was unable to do anything.</font>

210
00:13:49,240 --> 00:13:54,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she couldn't drive me away 
or protect her friends,</font>

211
00:13:54,420 --> 00:13:57,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">there's no way she could save XENOS.</font>

212
00:13:57,600 --> 00:14:00,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She grew up on Earth.</font>

213
00:14:00,280 --> 00:14:05,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It will take time for her to gain 
XENOS's, the Diva's, power.</font>

214
00:14:05,990 --> 00:14:12,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not everyone is strong, almighty, 
and perfect like you.</font>

215
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:16,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Of course, neither am I.</font>

216
00:14:19,110 --> 00:14:23,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Yes, Medea. You're inadequate.</i></font>

217
00:14:24,270 --> 00:14:28,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your loyalty to XENOS, 
your devotion to your duty.</font>

218
00:14:29,180 --> 00:14:32,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I devote my life to righteous duty.</font>

219
00:14:32,030 --> 00:14:36,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But does your decision 
fall under that category?</font>

220
00:14:37,350 --> 00:14:39,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You doubt my judgment?</font>

221
00:14:39,990 --> 00:14:43,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If she disappears, so does 
the hope for Earth.</font>

222
00:14:43,680 --> 00:14:46,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>This is a battle for survival 
to begin with.</i></font>

223
00:14:46,630 --> 00:14:49,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Erasing the hope of Earth has been our—</i></font>

224
00:14:49,660 --> 00:14:55,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And what we gain by that 
is temporary Idea to be used up.</font>

225
00:14:55,800 --> 00:14:58,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It is not the Idea of blessing</i></font>

226
00:14:58,820 --> 00:15:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>our Diva Lady Eden has produced 
that has supported us for years.</i></font>

227
00:15:04,380 --> 00:15:11,210
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>And you think this immature girl 
is capable of singing that blessing?</i></font>

228
00:15:11,210 --> 00:15:17,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>The tainted Diva who grew up 
on the tainted Earth?</i></font>

229
00:15:17,680 --> 00:15:22,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It is true that Earth may 
not have the order we do.</font>

230
00:15:23,190 --> 00:15:27,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're cumbersome, 
disorganized, and incohesive.</font>

231
00:15:27,690 --> 00:15:31,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're animals who release 
Idea uncontrollably.</font>

232
00:15:31,540 --> 00:15:34,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, they would look like 
pests in your eyes.</font>

233
00:15:35,790 --> 00:15:40,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But still, they produce 
Idea and improve each other.</font>

234
00:15:41,380 --> 00:15:44,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They're doing something we can't.</font>

235
00:15:47,610 --> 00:15:51,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You want to protect the blood of 
the Diva and the fate of Earth?</i></font>

236
00:15:52,310 --> 00:15:55,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You sound like Orphe.</i></font>

237
00:15:55,440 --> 00:15:57,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orphe was right.</font>

238
00:15:57,510 --> 00:16:00,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Haven't you come to realize 
he was right, too?</font>

239
00:16:00,930 --> 00:16:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>If she becomes Lady Eden's heir, 
XENOS will find its true salvation.</i></font>

240
00:16:06,600 --> 00:16:10,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It may take a long time, but both XENOS 
and the earthlings can be saved.</i></font>

241
00:16:10,820 --> 00:16:13,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The future Orphe dreamed of</font>

242
00:16:13,830 --> 00:16:16,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>can be achieved, do you not agree?!</i></font>

243
00:16:18,890 --> 00:16:22,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Orphe this, Orphe that.</font>

244
00:16:23,920 --> 00:16:26,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You also fell for that imbecile.</i></font>

245
00:16:27,500 --> 00:16:29,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>You were right, Samael.</i></font>

246
00:16:42,090 --> 00:16:42,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">The secondary?!</font>

247
00:16:47,310 --> 00:16:50,980
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Man, you just had to step 
on a landmine, didn't you?</font>

248
00:16:51,560 --> 00:16:58,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Samael, did you not find 
the earthlings amusing?</font>

249
00:16:59,380 --> 00:17:03,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Did you not see hope in them?</font>

250
00:17:03,610 --> 00:17:07,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's a different interpretation, Medea.</font>

251
00:17:07,780 --> 00:17:10,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I found hope...</font>

252
00:17:10,660 --> 00:17:13,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">in the Earth as a mighty foe.</font>

253
00:17:21,690 --> 00:17:23,190
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea-san?</font>

254
00:17:23,620 --> 00:17:28,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea, you said there was a way</font>

255
00:17:28,690 --> 00:17:33,200
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">to save both XENOS and the earthlings 
even if it'd take a long time.</font>

256
00:17:33,840 --> 00:17:38,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But the road to salvation 
must not be any longer, not even a step.</font>

257
00:17:38,910 --> 00:17:43,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If there's even the slightest 
possibility of a detour,</font>

258
00:17:44,410 --> 00:17:47,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">then I will not hesitate 
to save XENOS alone!</font>

259
00:17:59,450 --> 00:18:04,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Before you kill her, 
shouldn't we check in with Archon?</font>

260
00:18:04,510 --> 00:18:07,450
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She is kin to the Diva, after all.</font>

261
00:18:12,350 --> 00:18:13,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do as you wish.</font>

262
00:18:16,230 --> 00:18:18,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well then, now that that's over with...</font>

263
00:18:19,760 --> 00:18:22,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why don't you come with me, Miss Diva?</font>

264
00:18:25,300 --> 00:18:28,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I kindly gave you a chance for survival.</font>

265
00:18:28,340 --> 00:18:31,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You'd be better off doing exactly 
what you're told, you know?</font>

266
00:18:33,970 --> 00:18:36,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A chance for survival?</font>

267
00:18:37,620 --> 00:18:40,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah, because you're Eden the Diva's—</font>

268
00:18:40,690 --> 00:18:43,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is there a chance for Kyoya to survive?</font>

269
00:18:44,550 --> 00:18:45,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

270
00:18:45,870 --> 00:18:49,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">A chance for μ, Soji, June-san...</font>

271
00:18:50,300 --> 00:18:57,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">everyone at Harmonia, everyone 
Kyoya holds dear, to survive?</font>

272
00:19:00,250 --> 00:19:02,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Look at that.</i></font>

273
00:19:02,000 --> 00:19:05,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>She's shamefully begging for their lives!</i></font>

274
00:19:05,750 --> 00:19:06,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Tell me!</font>

275
00:19:08,350 --> 00:19:14,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If you stay here until the Mirage closes, 
then you disappear along with SI-VIS.</font>

276
00:19:14,920 --> 00:19:20,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You, SI-VIS, Harmonia, they all disappear 
from the memories of the world.</font>

277
00:19:20,840 --> 00:19:24,310
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we'll take this world 
without any resistance.</font>

278
00:19:24,680 --> 00:19:28,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's the exact outcome Apollo had in mind.</font>

279
00:19:28,400 --> 00:19:34,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But if you agree to my condition, 
you can hold on to a glimmer of hope.</font>

280
00:19:35,470 --> 00:19:42,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although that choice may be 
a double-edged sword for Earth.</font>

281
00:19:42,510 --> 00:19:43,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Your condition?</font>

282
00:19:58,410 --> 00:20:00,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't do it, Nagi.</font>

283
00:20:01,030 --> 00:20:05,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't listen to what they tell you.</font>

284
00:20:06,560 --> 00:20:08,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Kyoya!</font>

285
00:20:40,620 --> 00:20:41,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Here we go.</font>

286
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:44,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Don't you want to say goodbye?</font>

287
00:20:45,310 --> 00:20:46,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine.</font>

288
00:20:46,960 --> 00:20:49,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I know I'll be seeing him again very soon.</font>

289
00:20:56,790 --> 00:21:03,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Bring Pandora to Earth, and give 
the one-and-only Elpis to SI-VIS.</font>

290
00:21:04,450 --> 00:21:07,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Medea, you take this one.</font>

291
00:21:08,210 --> 00:21:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's getting exciting.</font>

292
00:21:10,630 --> 00:21:15,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">With our convictions at stake,
why don't we destroy each other?</font>

293
00:21:32,150 --> 00:21:32,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

294
00:21:34,100 --> 00:21:36,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that? Is it floating?</font>

295
00:21:36,140 --> 00:21:37,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's falling down!</font>

296
00:21:37,950 --> 00:21:40,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">G-Get out of here!</font>

297
00:21:47,100 --> 00:21:48,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nagi! Nagi!</font>

298
00:21:51,000 --> 00:21:53,290
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Move! Move!</font>

